summary: add player house which is inside the cave.Its located near to Karthwasten.
descriptionHtml:
Add player house which is inside the cave.its located near to Karthwasten.There is 3 floor(basement,1st floor and 2nd floor). Include 
-Smelter 
-Tanningrack 
-Workbench 
-Grindstone 
-Blacksmith force 
-Woodchopping block 
-All birthsign stones 
-Alchemy lab 
-Arcane Enchanter 
-Weapon racks,plaques and display cases 
-13x mannequins 
-Lots of chests 

If you find anything to fix let me know
(You can also subscribe this in steam, Just search "Underground Manor")
